author: Play On Tabletop
description:
Limited Edition T-shirt from Not a T-shirt Company! Play On swag and cool stuff available from Michael, the Merch Man's, official partner of Play On Tabletop. https://merch.playontabletop.com/ and check out his Instagram michaelbuckthorppaints.  The Limited Edition shirt that Tak is trying to have not exist will be available in very limited supply for two weeks or until we run out of supply (May 27 - June 10).

The Space Wolves have not forgiven the Grey Knights for what happened in the Months of Shame after the First War of Armageddon. In this battle Tak utilizes the new Wolf Guard Battle Leader, new Wolf Priest, new Blood Claws, new Grey Hunters, and new Wolf Guard Headtakers. Thank you so much Games Workshop for sending us early access to it all. Michael is excited to be part of the rivalry between Grey Knights and Space Wolves. Lists in the Description Below.

Thank you Games Workshop for sending us early access to the Space Wolves and Chapter Approved.
